Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「花映難波津 隆冬且暫隱」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.69,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なにわずに　さくやこのはな　ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「初春又將至 再綻此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:10.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的節目看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看了看了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生裡邊有模特綾瀨千歲的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 我是她的粉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該是超可愛的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 我們去看看吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個班?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽說每天午休時都在休息廳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨…千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}かるた（歌留多，骨牌）：用有畫的牌來進行的一種競技遊戲，\N競技歌留多使用小倉百人一首進行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競技歌留多部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 四 !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動服?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 那腰帶怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又穿成那種樣子…這麼不注重儀表!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是您說這種時候不能穿裙子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要穿運動服 就全身從上到下都只穿運動服!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你那傳單也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要貼的話只能貼一張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這裡脫!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:31.94,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你口口聲聲說要搞競技歌留多部 上古文課卻又一直在睡覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,説起來 別人說她雖然有張難得的漂亮臉蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要一活動一開口 形象就全毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人稱「白搭美女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:53.02,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(559,213)\blur11\fad(984,1013)}再綻此花矣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歌留多」什麼的就放棄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是一起玩田徑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短跑都進市比賽了 太可惜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多是…「禍福皆因強出頭」那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}原文是「犬も歩けば棒にあたる」，\N出現在古典版的競技歌留多中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說田徑部應該叫「邂逅系」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邂逅系?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該去參加活動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然前輩又要生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見啦 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那個前輩啊 可真夠恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊… 有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來都決心一定要在高中找到同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百投入歌留多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 綾瀨就是女王了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}女王（クイーン），指在全國歌留多比賽中，授予\N參加女性組比賽並獲得日本第一名的人的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:05.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「誰為我知己 未語可知心…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:05.55,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}たれをかも　しるひとにせむ　たかさごの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正覺得玩歌留多很快樂 是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你總這樣「大」字躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會被人說成是「白搭美女」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:17.36,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「高砂松雖壽 不及故人情」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:17.36,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}まつもむかしの　ともならなくに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一居然在同一個高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你一定直升進名校的高中部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單程要一個半小時才能到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要接著讀3年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說剛才那下很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是千早你考上都立的好高中 讓我很意外…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們根本沒差多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會再長的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也還會再長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一太一太一 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你不怎麼受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在? 在車站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 你在分倍河原車站等嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 有女朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點受打擊了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被告白了我才和她交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那麼的喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新也找到了比歌留多更重要的事嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和新…有聯繫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年連賀年卡也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…好像去年也沒參加全國大會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學在田徑部 也沒參加過近江神宮的全國大會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}最高級別的全國大會基本都在近江神宮舉行，\N因此也被稱為競技歌留多的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加田徑部 不也很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 高中會做些其他事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多終究只是興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 太一不玩歌留多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得在同一所高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中學也是以足球部為主的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能永遠玩歌留多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「誰為我知己 未語可知心」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:09.36,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たれをかも　しるひとにせむ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首和歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說以前的朋友都已經不在了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續玩下去的話就能再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要再見面啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前 在東京
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我 還未曾找到熱衷的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 你姐姐的選美比賽如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然闖進了最後一輪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 明天的報紙會刊登姐姐的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早的姐姐很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太一也這麼想?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和千早不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你就只有運動能趕得上我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有身高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 想打架嗎 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個轉校生根本不說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和那傢伙扯上關係比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說那傢伙把虫當零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班有人看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袜子上還有洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班不需要他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把綿谷的福井方言記下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最近他都不說話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有新東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很小氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 那次啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是綿谷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會跟為了嘲笑他而記筆記的人說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也…不是想那麼做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎? 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你忘記拿路線表啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說記住了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天才剛開始做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可有200多家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別送錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2丁目5區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原先生和他對面的5家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大澤 藤宮 山本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內山先生退訂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫田公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,101 103 203 204
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一家 綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐上報紙了哦 快醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 還有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正還是落選了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能入選最後15人也很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把這個照片給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:11:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這個得大獎的人身材確實更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別總這麼說話不經大腦啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 我看新聞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 好厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厲害 真的登了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 明明是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早卻還是像個男孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}百人一首：收集一百位歌人各一首的和歌集，\N一般指最出名的「小倉百人一首」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位 百人一首的貼紙集齊沒有?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百首都記住了的話 就來參加測試哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不可能的啦 你記住多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}才記住10首 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住的人就可以參加下個月的歌留多比賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.88,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}15個~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.22,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這也沒差多少吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你記住多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多才到一半吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了 學習比不過你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島同學 你已經完全記住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是什麼都做得來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不只是真島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班還有一個人 也記住了全部一百首哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天放學以後 綿谷同學來參加測試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣背出了一百首哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好厲害~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真的是一口氣背下來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個月的歌留多大會 你也會出場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送報紙的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷同學早上送報紙了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然送報紙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生是不允許打工的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…綿谷同學 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有叫我幫忙的時候…才去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為家裡太窮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 他一直都穿同一條裤子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷同學很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能送報紙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也要加油把一百首都背下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見咯 真島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 把你唯一的行頭弄濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要穿的衣服沒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆問媽媽借裙子穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到你會做這麼過份的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你為何總是幫他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要這樣 說不定明天起也會被孤立的哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會不管你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,説真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說隨便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你就算哭我也不管!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好破啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人就是說話不經大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上也是因為這個挨了姐姐一腳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…可以說話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會記筆記的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼早上…要等報紙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐參加了選美大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早點看到那個報導
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的這個人就是我姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吧 厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想 就是有一天姐姐能成為日本第一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種是不能稱之為夢想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自己的事情 就不算是夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以把夢想寄托在別人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你姐姐就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那綿谷同學有什麼夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於你自己的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這不就是百人一首嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說會不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校每年都會舉辦歌留多大會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 今天老師不也說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我…我們來比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 但是沒有人來讀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有磁帶啊 磁帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…怎麼弄來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把25張牌分成三段排好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到上句讀出來 就要拿掉下句對應的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}上句（上の句），指短歌的前半五·七·五三句，\N下句（下の句）則指剩下的第四、第五句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在才只背下來50個左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只是個歌留多比賽而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種眼神 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋來紅葉散…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.59,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あらしふく…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天工織做錦 還綴龍田川」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:29.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,662)}たつたのかはの　にしきなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又扎到門裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今時辛酸淚 老來潤心田」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:42.83,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ながらへば　またこのごろや　しのばれむ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:54.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「世間千般愁 欲解竟無方」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:54.46,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}よのなかよ　みちこそなけれ　おもひいる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多…以前是這樣玩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要搶到一張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張牌的上句我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「激流戲淺水 岩前兩紛飛」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.58,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}せをはやみ　いはにせかるる　たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要搶到那一張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有那一張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要搶到!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.68,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「激…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:38.68,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:51.81,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「…流戲淺水 岩前兩紛飛」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:51.81,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}…をはやみ　いはにせかるる　たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從綿谷同學那裡搶到一張了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這算什麼啊 強得過頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是綾瀨同學也搶到了一張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這一張啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我很開心!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在福井的時候 經常和朋友們一起玩歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 東京卻沒什麼人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是一個人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人? 聽著磁帶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多在其他國家都沒什麼人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為確實比較難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這也就意味著…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本取得第一的話 就是世界第一了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…第一?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加歌留多比賽 成為名人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}名人：與女王相對，是授予男性的\N代表歌留多日本第一名稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千早」…是個好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這是屬於你的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張牌的上句 是以「神代有蓬萊」開頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.73,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,658)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽到「ちはや」就要搶這張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.82,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,660)}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}ちはやぶる，日文漢字可以寫成「千早振」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這張牌就是「ちはや」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.78,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,660)}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的眼中就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 這是你的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 女朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小女朋友 吃地瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬萊 今看龍田川」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:50.10,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちはやぶる　かみよもきかず　たつたがは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真的好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇景未曾見 江攬紅葉衫」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.70,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,からくれなゐに　みづくくるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和新玩歌留多的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知道的不是歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是新的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:22:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
